node.text:
🌸THE May flower 🌸 , 23 years ago my mother went into an early labor with me.. she was on bed rest while pregnant , we almost lost our lives, I was born the day after Mother’s Day in the year 1998. It was a miracle. Every few years my birthday lands on Mother’s Day and we are able to celebrate such a beautiful day together. She always tells me how when she looked outside the hospital windows while holding me she had seen all the mama animals having their spring time babies , Deers , bunnies , bears - all of it , the sun was shining and I was brought into this earth holding the greatest gift from God himself , One amongst we all share together as a unity ... LIFE! I am so thankful to be here and to be able to experience all the beautiful things life truly has to offer. I am feeling beyond blessed & loved by all my loved ones. I’m so thankful and grateful for everything God has in store for this next chapter in life. The second greatest gift(s) I received in this lifetime was my husband , my family & my friends❤️🙏🏼 to be able to love so unconditionally and have this bond with other human beings is so surreal and filling. Thank you to all of my loved ones & to all of you for making my life , this weekend & especially this wonderful big day so special. I love you all so so much. Happy birthday to me ! 💖🌟🌟💖💖🐥💜💜💜 

Special thanks to these bad ass woman for this epic photo shoot! My friend Crystal on the florals , Keshia on the hair & Daria for making the vision come to life. 🙏🏼 this was so much fun to capture and even funner to all be hands on with the creative direction. Love y’all!
